com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.eval

Class ASTSearchInSearchOptimizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.optimizers.AbstractJoinGroupOptimizer
      • com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast.eval.ASTSearchInSearchOptimizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IASTOptimizer

    public class ASTSearchInSearchOptimizer
extends AbstractJoinGroupOptimizer
    Converts a BDS.SEARCH_IN_SEARCH function call (inside a filter) into an IN filter using the full text index to determine the IN set. Convert: 
     filter((?o,"foo")) .
    To: 
     filter(?o IN ("foo", "foo bar", "hello foo", ...)) .
    This is a way of using the full text index to filter instead of using regex.
